# Environment Variables Quick Reference

## Required for Choreo Deployment

```bash
# Azure OpenAI
AZURE_OPENAI_KEY=your-api-key-here
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-4
AZURE_OPENAI_EMBEDDINGS_DEPLOYMENT=text-embedding-ada-002

# Milvus Vector Database
MILVUS_URI=https://your-cluster.milvus.io:19530
MILVUS_TOKEN=token:your-token-here
```

## Optional Configuration

```bash
# Azure OpenAI Advanced
AZURE_OPENAI_API_VERSION=2024-02-15-preview

# Milvus Advanced
MILVUS_COLLECTION_NAME=choreo_developer_assistant
MILVUS_DIMENSION=1536
MILVUS_METRIC=COSINE

# GitHub Integration
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here

# Google Vision (for image processing)
GOOGLE_VISION_API_KEY=your-google-api-key

# Performance Tuning
ENABLE_LLM_SUMMARIZATION=true
MAX_SUMMARIZATION_RETRIES=2
ENABLE_URL_VALIDATION=true
URL_VALIDATION_TIMEOUT=5
URL_VALIDATION_TRUSTED_DOMAINS=github.com,wso2.com,choreo.dev

# Python Runtime
PYTHONPATH=/app
PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1
```

## Configuration in Choreo

In Choreo Console, go to:
**Component Settings** → **Environment Variables** → **Add Variable**

For sensitive values (API keys, tokens), mark as **Secret**.

